divs: sighting detailson clear sky days, i take pictures to record whatever may be overhead. the pictures are then zoom inspected on the computer. attached is a photo taken at 1:04 pm today (5\20\09). when you zoom in on the object, you can see sun light reflecting off of it. the blurring indicates the object was moving very fast. camera: canon sd630 digital elph 6 mega pixel; shutter speed 15-1\1500 sec location: my back yard view direction: ene note: i did not see the object in the sky .... only on the photo.
